textContent:
---always missing u---

Halu my bby! I just want you to know that I miss you with every passing moment and that I really do think that my life's always happier when I'm with you! 

I'm so sad that I don't get to Trinoma with you tomorrow huhuhu, pero at the same time, I feel super blessed kase I feel so loved by you kase kawawa rugo bby ko, nangcry rugo siya kase di niya ko makakasama HUHUHUHU ABABAYU MY BABYYYY. I LOVE YOU SO MUCH!!! Bili kita pasalubong oki!! And don't worry! Forever na tayo magkasama and mapupuntahan rin natin lahat ng malls and other places na gusto naten mapuntahan together! Abababyu mwaa!!
